snippet.title: ABM Command - Gameplay - Windows 3.1 (1993)
snippet.description:
Watch me play the 1993 Windows 3.x game called ABM Command. It is a clone of the Atari arcade game Missile Command. It was programmed by Kent Rollins.

NOTE: The video doesn't contain sound.
